  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Madlein is a ‘state-of-the-art’ design hotel in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/3c3783ff0696436cb752c8195e705dec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3c3783ff0696436cb752c8195e705dec}" title="Ischgl">Ischgl</a>, and has won many awards for its contemporary atmosphere and décor. Minimalist Zen design is the common theme that runs through the hotel decor, which oozes a calm and wellbeing feeling that starts as soon as you enter the lobby. The facilities are superb, after skiing, relax in the extensive spa area. After dinner, dance the night away in the in-house nightclub.</p>]]></description>
